        "\n",
        "\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from sklearn import datasets\n",
        "from sklearn.svm import SVC\n",
        "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, GridSearchCV, cross_val_score\n",
        "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler\n",
        "from sklearn.decomposition import PCA\n",
        "\n",
        "#Dataset\n",
        "cancer = datasets.load_breast_cancer()\n",
        "X = cancer.data\n",
        "y = cancer.target\n",
        "\n",
        "# Scaling the data\n",
        "scaler = StandardScaler()\n",
        "X_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(X)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Split into train and test\n",
        "X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X_scaled, y, test_size=0.25, random_state=42)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Linear SVM\n",
        "linear_svm = SVC(kernel='linear', C=1.0)\n",
        "linear_svm.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
        "print(f'Linear SVM Accuracy: {linear_svm.score(X_test, y_test):.4f}')\n",
        "\n",
        "# RBF SVM\n",
        "rbf_svm = SVC(kernel='rbf', C=1.0, gamma='scale')\n",
        "rbf_svm.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
        "print(f'RBF SVM Accuracy: {rbf_svm.score(X_test, y_test):.4f}')\n",
        "\n",
        "#Hyperparameter\n",
        "param_grid = {\n",
        "    'C': [0.1, 1, 10],\n",
        "    'gamma': ['scale', 0.01, 0.1, 1]\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "grid = GridSearchCV(SVC(kernel='rbf'), param_grid, cv=5)\n",
        "grid.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f'Best params: {grid.best_params_}')\n",
        "print(f'Best CV score: {grid.best_score_:.4f}')\n",
        "print(f'Test accuracy with best params: {grid.score(X_test, y_test):.4f}')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Cross-validation\n",
        "cv_scores = cross_val_score(grid.best_estimator_, X_scaled, y, cv=5)\n",
        "print(f'Cross-validated accuracy: {cv_scores.mean():.4f} (+/- {cv_scores.std():.4f})')\n",
        "\n",
        "#PCA(2D projection)\n",
        "pca = PCA(n_components=2)\n",
        "X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X_scaled)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Retrain on PCA components for visualization\n",
        "svm_vis = SVC(kernel='rbf', C=grid.best_params_['C'], gamma=grid.best_params_['gamma'])\n",
        "svm_vis.fit(X_pca, y)\n",
        "\n",
        "def plot_svm_boundary(model, X_proj, y_proj):\n",
        "    h = .02\n",
        "    x_min, x_max = X_proj[:, 0].min() - 1, X_proj[:, 0].max() + 1\n",
        "    y_min, y_max = X_proj[:, 1].min() - 1, X_proj[:, 1].max() + 1\n",
        "    xx, yy = np.meshgrid(np.arange(x_min, x_max, h),\n",
        "                         np.arange(y_min, y_max, h))\n",
        "    Z = model.predict(np.c_[xx.ravel(), yy.ravel()])\n",
        "    Z = Z.reshape(xx.shape)\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))\n",
        "    plt.contourf(xx, yy, Z, alpha=0.3, cmap=plt.cm.coolwarm)\n",
        "    plt.scatter(X_proj[:, 0], X_proj[:, 1], c=y_proj, edgecolors='k', cmap=plt.cm.coolwarm)\n",
        "    plt.title('SVM Decision Boundary (PCA projection)')\n",
        "    plt.xlabel('PCA 1')\n",
        "    plt.ylabel('PCA 2')\n",
        "    plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "plot_svm_boundary(svm_vis, X_pca, y)"
      ],
